defaultANNEX Ddefault&#xa0;defaultADVISORY COMMITTEE ON DANGEROUS PATHOGENSdefault&#xa0;defaultGuidance on prevention of CJD and vCJD by Advisory Committee on Dangerous Pathogens' Transmissible Spongiform Encephalopathy (ACDP TSE) Subgroup.default&#xa0;defaultThe following ACDP guidance documents are all publically available at:
